  "env_id": "electrical_calculations_env@0.1",
  "description": "Calculate the output pulse width of a 555 timer in Monostable mode using the Electrical Engineering Calculations app. Use a resistor (R) value of 470 kΩ and a capacitor (C) value of 100 µF. Save the calculated numeric value in seconds to /sdcard/tasks/555_timer_monostable/result.txt.",
